# extendedLogDataStringEncoding

**Instance Property**

The string encoding of the extended log data.

## Declaration

```swift
var extendedLogDataStringEncoding: UInt { get }
```

## Accessing error data

- **events**: A chronologically ordered array of player item error log event objects.
- **extendedLogData()**: Returns a serialized representation of the error log in the Extended Log File Format.
